21 Layer Air Fryer Nachos
Layers below (makes a lot of nachos)

2 bags of Doritos (you chose the flavor)
2 cups salsa verde
1 pound tacos seasoned ground beef
1 cup black beans
4 cups grated Mexican blended cheese
